data.description: Location, Location, location! This home sits on a very large cul-de-sac lot right in the middle of town. this is a split bedroom floor plan with an oversized master bedroom with a sliding door that leads to the back patio, walk in closet with a high vaulted ceiling, the 2 additional bedrooms are good sized rooms with deep closets. the 4th bedroom is a large oversized room that could also function as a media room or home office. In the kitchen you will find lots of natural light, a walk-in pantry and stainless-steel appliances. The Appliances are completely new. HVAC installed new in this 2023. for landscaping and a large patio to enjoy the oversized yard. call for a showing today
